sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant BE as FastAPI Backend
    participant SQL as SQL Statement API
    participant FS as Files API (Volumes)
    participant DR as Data Rooms API
    participant GC as Genie Conversation API

    rect rgb(220, 235, 255)
        Note over U,GC: Phase 1 — File Upload & Table Creation (per-user schema)

        U->>FE: Upload CSV / Excel file
        FE->>BE: POST /api/upload (multipart form)
        activate BE

        Note right of BE: Resolve user identity from<br/>proxy headers (X-Forwarded-Email)<br/>Derive per-user schema name

        BE->>SQL: CREATE SCHEMA IF NOT EXISTS<br/>catalog.user_schema
        activate SQL
        SQL-->>BE: status OK
        deactivate SQL

        BE->>SQL: CREATE VOLUME IF NOT EXISTS<br/>catalog.user_schema.raw_upload
        activate SQL
        SQL-->>BE: status OK
        deactivate SQL

        BE->>FS: PUT /api/2.0/fs/files<br/>Upload raw file to Volume
        activate FS
        FS-->>BE: Upload complete
        deactivate FS

        BE->>SQL: CREATE OR REPLACE TABLE ... AS<br/>SELECT * FROM read_files(volume_path)
        activate SQL
        SQL-->>BE: status OK
        deactivate SQL

        BE->>SQL: DESCRIBE TABLE + SELECT COUNT(*)
        activate SQL
        SQL-->>BE: column_info, row_count
        deactivate SQL

        BE-->>FE: table_name, columns, row_count
        deactivate BE
        FE-->>U: Show table preview + schema
    end

    rect rgb(220, 255, 230)
        Note over U,GC: Phase 2 — Genie Space Creation

        FE->>BE: POST /api/genie/create-space
        activate BE
        BE->>DR: POST /api/2.0/data-rooms/<br/>display_name, warehouse_id,<br/>table_identifiers, run_as_type
        activate DR
        DR-->>BE: space_id
        deactivate DR
        BE-->>FE: space_id
        deactivate BE
        FE-->>U: Transition to Chat Interface
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 215)
        Note over U,GC: Phase 3 — Natural Language Query (repeatable)

        U->>FE: Type a question
        FE->>BE: POST /api/genie/ask<br/>space_id, question
        activate BE

        alt First message in conversation
            BE->>GC: genie.start_conversation_and_wait()
            activate GC
            GC->>GC: Generate SQL & execute
            GC-->>BE: conversation_id, message_id, attachments
            deactivate GC
        else Follow-up message
            BE->>GC: genie.create_message_and_wait()<br/>conversation_id, content
            activate GC
            GC->>GC: Generate SQL & execute (with context)
            GC-->>BE: message_id, attachments
            deactivate GC
        end

        BE->>GC: genie.get_message_query_result_by_attachment()
        activate GC
        GC-->>BE: columns, rows
        deactivate GC

        BE-->>FE: sql_query, data_rows, text_response
        deactivate BE
        FE->>FE: Render data table
        FE->>FE: Auto-generate chart from data
        FE-->>U: Display table + chart + text answer
    end
